---
title: Grilled Honey Tofu Wraps with Potato Wedges
description: Classic pub flavours are all wrapped up into a delicious handheld! Tender tofu is grilled to perfection for that smoky, chargrilled flavour, then tossed in spiced honey. Creamy ranch and quick-pickled cucumbers make these wraps lip-smacking good!
